---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---
<PageLayout title="About">
  <section class="intro">
    <h2 class="tagline">Hi, I'm Alex ‚Äî <span class="accent">engine dev & systems generalist</span>.</h2>
    <p class="lede">I build the foundations players rarely see but always feel: rendering backends, low‚Äëlevel networking, audio pipelines, performance tooling, asset flows & the glue that keeps it all shippable. I enjoy turning complex subsystems into something teams can iterate on with confidence.</p>
    <div class="profile-links">
      <a href="https://github.com/AlexMollard" class="btn" rel="me" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/alex-mollard" class="btn" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
      <a href="/" class="btn secondary">Portfolio</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="stack">
    <h3>Core Stack</h3>
    <ul class="badges">
      <li>C++</li>
      <li>Vulkan</li>
      <li>GLSL</li>
      <li>HLSL</li>
      <li>CMake</li>
      <li>OpenGL</li>
      <li>C</li>
      <li>Clang</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
  <section class="breadth">
    <h3>Across the Engine</h3>
    <ul class="areas">
      <li><strong>Rendering:</strong> Vulkan + legacy OpenGL paths, shader toolchains (GLSL/HLSL), frame pacing & GPU profiling.</li>
      <li><strong>Engine Systems:</strong> asset build / hot‚Äëreload flows, memory tracking, job systems, build configuration (CMake) & platform abstraction.</li>
      <li><strong>Low‚Äëlevel Networking:</strong> real‚Äëtime state sync, bandwidth/latency trade‚Äëoffs, reliability layers atop UDP, instrumentation.</li>
      <li><strong>Audio:</strong> spatial mixing chains, streaming & voice allocation, performance budgeting.</li>
      <li><strong>Tooling & Performance:</strong> frame capture analysis, CPU/GPU timing aggregation, fast iteration pipelines.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="studio">
    <h3>Day Job</h3>
    <p>At <strong>Big Ant Studios</strong> I tend to work on ‚Äúwhatever moves the game forward‚Äù: from engine internals to rendering polish, performance hunts, build reliability, feature scaffolding and the occasional emergency fix minutes before a milestone. Wearing many hats keeps me honest about trade‚Äëoffs and developer experience.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="collab">
    <h3>Let's Collaborate</h3>
    <p>If you're exploring a rendering path, prototyping an engine feature, chasing a perf cliff or just want to chat about systems architecture ‚Äî reach out. Happy to pair, brainstorm or review.</p>
  </section>

  <blockquote class="quote">üí¨ "Code is like humour. When you have to explain it, it's bad." <span class="author">‚Äî Cory House</span></blockquote>

  <hr />
  <p class="fine-print">This site stays intentionally lean: no trackers, minimal JS islands, content first.</p>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .intro { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:1rem; }
  .tagline { font-size:clamp(1.4rem,3.2vw,2rem); margin:0; font-weight:600; }
  .tagline .accent { color: var(--color-accent); }
  .lede { font-size:1.05rem; max-width:60ch; }
  .profile-links { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:.65rem; margin-top:.25rem; }
  .btn { background:var(--color-accent); color:#fff; padding:.55rem .9rem; font-size:.85rem; font-weight:500; border-radius:var(--radius-sm); display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:.4rem; box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm); transition:background-color .25s var(--ease), transform .25s var(--ease); }
  .btn:hover { text-decoration:none; background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--color-accent),#7ab9ff); transform:translateY(-2px); }
  .btn.secondary { background:var(--color-bg-alt); color:var(--color-fg); border:1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .btn.secondary:hover { background:var(--color-code); }
  .stack { margin-top:2.5rem; }
  .badges { list-style:none; padding:0; margin:0; display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:.5rem; }
  .badges li { background:var(--color-bg-alt); border:1px solid var(--color-border); padding:.4rem .7rem; font-size:.7rem; letter-spacing:.5px; font-weight:500; border-radius:999px; text-transform:uppercase; position:relative; animation:fadeIn .6s ease; }
  @keyframes fadeIn { from {opacity:0; transform:translateY(4px);} to {opacity:1; transform:translateY(0);} }
  .breadth { margin-top:2.5rem; }
  .areas { list-style: none; padding:0; margin:1rem 0 0; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:.85rem; }
  .areas li { background:var(--color-bg-alt); border:1px solid var(--color-border); padding:.85rem 1rem; border-radius:var(--radius-md); line-height:1.45; }
  .studio { margin-top:2.75rem; }
  .collab { margin-top:2.75rem; }
  blockquote.quote { font-style:italic; font-size:1rem; background:var(--color-bg-alt); }
  blockquote.quote .author { display:block; margin-top:.35rem; font-style:normal; font-size:.85rem; opacity:.75; }
  .fine-print { font-size:.8rem; opacity:.65; }
  .small { font-size:.7rem; }
  @media (max-width:640px) { .profile-links { gap:.5rem; } .btn { font-size:.75rem; padding:.5rem .75rem; } }
</style>
